### PHP CodeSniffer

[PHP CodeSniffer Documentation](https://github.com/squizlabs/PHP_CodeSniffer/wiki). This tool helps to follow coding style and avoid common PHP coding mistakes.

#### Run

```bash
$ composer phpcs
```

